"Ahhh, this porridge is just right," she said happily, and she ate it all up.\
After she'd eaten the three bears' breakfasts, she decided she was feeling a little tired.\'a0 So, she walked into the living room where she saw three chairs.\'a0 Goldilocks sat in the first chair to rest her feet.\'a0\'a0\
