"Someone's been sleeping in my bed and she's still there!" exclaimed Baby bear.\uc0\u8232 \u8232 Just then, Goldilocks woke up and saw the three bears.\'a0 She screamed, "Help!"\'a0 And she jumped up and ran out of the room.\'a0 Goldilocks ran down the stairs, opened the door, and ran away into the forest.\'a0 And she never returned to the home of the three bears.\
